> This license is bilingual. In case of discrepancy or conflict
> between the Chinese and English versions, the Chinese version prevails.

## 一、许可范围澄清 / 1. Scope Clarification

上方 MIT 正文中的 "without restriction" 系标准协议文本原文，
其范围受本附加条款限制。本软件授权仅限于学习、研究与
个人非商业用途。以下行为不视为本许可授权范围：

- 将本仓库代码嵌入商业产品或服务
- 在生产环境中部署或使用
- 用于安全关键系统（医疗、航空、工业控制、自动驾驶等）
- 其他任何直接或间接营利性使用

**明确允许的非商业使用场景**（无需额外许可）：

- 个人自学、练习、面试准备
- 高等院校或培训机构内的非营利教学活动
- 学术论文、技术博客中的代码引用（须保留版权声明）
- 开源社区的技术讨论与代码审查

## Scope Clarification (English)

The term "without restriction" in the MIT text above is standard
boilerplate language. Its scope is limited by these Additional Terms.
The rights granted hereunder are limited to educational, research,
and personal non-commercial purposes. The following are NOT within
the scope of this license:

- Embedding this code in commercial products or services
- Deployment or use in production environments
- Use in safety-critical systems (medical, aviation,
  industrial control, autonomous driving, etc.)
- Any other direct or indirect commercial use

**Non-commercial uses explicitly permitted** (no additional permission):

- Personal study, practice, and interview preparation
- Non-profit teaching in academic or training settings
- Code citation in academic papers or technical articles
  (with copyright notice retained)
- Technical discussion and code review in open-source communities

